description: Beautifully and meticulously maintained home in Millstone Creek! Popular ''Everett'' model. Walking distance to Millstone Creek Park and walking/biking trails. Updated flooring in kitchen and entry space. Kitchen has granite countertops with stainless steel appliances and refinished cabinets. Rear living room with gas fireplace overlooks the beautiful backyard with paver patio and views of the pond. First floor laundry room and den for extra room or home office. Four large bedrooms upstairs. Fully finished basement has a bar space and extra FULL bathroom. Lower level great as a home theater area, exercise/rec or game room. Unfinished space for extra storage area as well. Come take a look!

description: BEAUTIFUL HOME IN A BEAUTIFUL NEIGHBORHOOD! This spacious home spanning over 2,000 sq. ft. is the perfect place to gather in numbers! With a generous sized deck, and finished basement, this home makes for an entertainers dream. Featuring 4 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, and a powder room this is a home one can plant roots! This home has been given so much love to prepare for its new owner/s. Updates include: New Carpet and paint throughout the entire home, new sink and countertops in kitchen, as well as new countertops and shower in the primary en suite bathroom, as well as new countertops and bathtub in the upper hall bath. The wooded lot just across the street North of the home has recently been purchased by Blendon Metro Parks. This truly is, a MUST SEE!

description: Gorgeous home located in Highland Lakes East.  Soaring two story Great room w/laminate wood flooring & tile surround gas fireplace opens to a large Dining Room.  Chef's Kitchen featuring white cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, gas range & tile floors.  Oversized 1st floor Owner's suite w/walk in closet & updated Owners bath featuring tile floors, frameless tile shower, whirlpool tub & double vanity w/granite counter.  Updated powder bath. 1st floor laundry.  Spacious Guest Bedrooms, updated bath & loft/office.  Newly finished lower level w/Family Room, Bedroom & full bath.  New Roof-2020.  New Furnace-2020.  Lovely rear yard, beautiful landscaping and two tiered deck for entertaining.  Fantastic location to Polaris, Uptown Westerville, Westerville bike paths, schools & parks.  A 10!

description: Great Location! Updated 4 BR, 2.5 BA home on a kid friendly cul-de-sac! Large front porch welcomes guests inside generous entry flanked by a Den/Office w/built-ins and formal Living Room/Dining Room. Newly remodeled open Kitchen features granite counters, coffee nook & custom pantry. Bayed Breakfast Rm opens to Family Rm w/brick floor-ceiling wood-burning FP, raised hearth, built-ins and wooden ceiling beams. Remodeled Powder Rm and Laundry completes the 1st Fl. Upstairs Owner's Suite has walk-in closet & bath w/heated floors, 3 additional BRs & Bath. See Improvements in Documents, including LVP floors throughout 1st Fl. Gather w/friends on patio, enjoy the custom-built fire pit or relax in the hot tub under Pergola. Close to Highlands Park/Pool, Uptown, Innis Woods, and Hoover Reservoir.

description: Welcome to the Erie floorplan: A 2-story traditional home, with covered front porch, two and one-half baths, and 3 to 4-bedrooms. Choose the full porch on the traditional elevation, or select the farmhouse elevation, with full front porch and board and batten siding, or the craftsman elevation, with tapered decorative columns, and shake and stone accents. Enter into the foyer from the covered front porch. Notice the flex room which can be used as a formal dining area, children's play area or select the study with double doors for a private home office. As you wander to the back of the home, to the side, you will find the powder room and guest coat closet.
